Our Services

  • Homepage

With over 40 years of experience in healthcare, Dr. Joseph Rosado, MD, MBA is not just a physician—he’s a leader in both conventional and alternative medicine. 

His deep expertise spans from emergency medical care and internal medicine to groundbreaking alternative treatments like medical cannabis, CBD therapy, and ketamine-assisted psychotherapy.

Call or Text Us!
(888) 971-5577

Why Patients Trust Dr. Rosado?

Award-Winning Physician & Speaker

Recognized nationally and internationally for his contributions to medicine.

Multidisciplinary Expertise

Experience as a paramedic, college professor, physician executive, and clinical researcher.

Innovative & Evidence-Based Treatments

Blending the best of traditional and modern medicine for optimal results.

Book An Appointment

Your health is complex. Your treatment should be, too

Comprehensive Clinical Services

1 %
Customer Satisfaction is Our Success

Dr. Joseph Rosado offers a comprehensive range of medical services, combining conventional medicine, advanced diagnostics, and alternative therapies to provide personalized, science-backed care. 

Whether you’re dealing with a chronic condition, pain management, or mental health concerns, Dr. Rosado creates tailored treatment plans that address your unique needs.

Book An Appointment
We Provide the Best Service for your Health

Our Practice Areas and Expertise

Internal Medicine – Managing Complex Illnesses with Precision

As a specialist in internal medicine, Dr. Joseph Rosado has the scientific knowledge and clinical expertise to diagnose, treat, and manage serious illnesses and multi-system diseases. 

What Does Internal Medicine Cover?

Comprehensive Diagnosis & Treatment – Managing complex conditions affecting multiple organ systems.
Personalized Care for Chronic Diseases – Hypertension, diabetes, cardiovascular issues, and more.
Preventive & Holistic Approach – Addressing root causes rather than just symptoms.
Book Dr. Rosado

Advanced Diagnostics – The Key to Accurate Treatment

Diagnostic tests play a crucial role in identifying, monitoring, and treating medical conditions. Dr. Rosado leverages advanced diagnostic tools to pinpoint underlying health issues, ensuring accurate treatment plans tailored to each patient.

Why Diagnostics Matter

Early Detection – Catching illnesses before they progress.
Treatment – Ensuring the right care from the start.
Ongoing Monitoring – Tracking improvements and adjusting treatments accordingly.
Book Dr. Rosado

Medical Cannabis & CBD Therapy – Natural Relief for Pain & Wellness

Dr. Rosado is a recognized expert in medical cannabis and CBD therapy, offering safe, legal, and effective solutions for patients suffering from chronic pain, PTSD, anxiety, and neurological conditions. His expertise ensures that every patient receives a personalized treatment plan designed to maximize benefits while minimizing risks.

How Can Medical Cannabis & CBD Help?

Reduces Chronic Pain & Inflammation
Supports Mental Health Conditions Like PTSD & Anxiety
Improves Sleep, Mood, and Overall Well-Being
Book Dr. Rosado

Mental & Behavioral Health – A Holistic Approach to Psychological Well-being

Mental and behavioral health issues affect millions of people, yet many struggle to find effective, long-term solutions. Dr. Rosado provides comprehensive, science-backed treatment options, combining conventional mental health care with innovative alternative therapies like ketamine-assisted psychotherapy and medical cannabis.

What Conditions Can Be Treated?

Anxiety, Depression, and PTSD
Behavioral and Emotional Disorders
Substance Use & Addiction Recovery Support
Book Dr. Rosado

PRP Therapy (Autologous Conditioned Plasma) – Regenerative Healing

Platelet-Rich Plasma (PRP) therapy is a cutting-edge regenerative treatment that uses your own blood’s healing properties to repair damaged muscles, tendons, ligaments, and joints. 

PRP therapy stimulates cellular regeneration and accelerates tissue repair, making it an excellent option for patients seeking non-surgical recovery solutions

Benefits of PRP Therapy

Speeds Up Recovery for Injuries & Chronic Pain
Minimally Invasive with Long-Lasting Results
Reduces Inflammation & Enhances Mobility
Book Dr. Rosado

Personalized Treatment Plans

At Joseph Rosado, MD, LLC, patient care is never one-size-fits-all. Whether you need help managing a chronic illness, recovering from an injury, or improving your mental well-being, Dr. Rosado creates customized treatment plans that combine traditional medicine with alternative therapies to deliver lasting results.

What Makes This Approach Different?

Tailored to Your Specific Health Needs – Every treatment is designed for your body and condition.
Evidence-Based & Innovative – Using the latest research in medical cannabis, ketamine therapy, and functional medicine.
A Holistic & Preventive Focus – Treating the root cause, not just the symptoms.
Book Dr. Rosado
1

Schedule
An Appointment

Call, text, email, or fill out the appt request form on our website and our medical team will follow up.
2

Fill Out
Our Intake Forms

Provide your medical history including any medications along with the reason(s) you are seeking treatment.
3

Meet With
Dr. Rosado

Discuss health concerns, goals, and uncover the root of any health problems and receive a personalized care plan.
4

Follow Your
Wellness Plan

Begin your health and wellness improvement plan with medical guidance every step of the way.

Proven Results

Real Patient Success Stories

When conventional medicine failed, these patients turned to Dr. Rosado for answers—and found life-changing results. His science-backed treatments have helped thousands regain control over their health, proving that a different approach can make all the difference.

After years of struggling with PTSD and medication that didn’t work, I finally found relief with medical cannabis. Dr. Rosado guided me every step of the way, and I finally feel like myself again

Sarah L

I had lost hope after trying every antidepressant available. Ketamine therapy with Dr. Rosado changed everything. Within weeks, my depression lifted for the first time in years.

Michael S

Traditional treatments weren’t helping my chronic pain. Functional medicine and IV therapy gave me back my energy, and I’m no longer dependent on painkillers.

Miona G

Dr. Rosado is a fantastic holistic doctor. He actually takes the time to listen to you and makes specific health recommendations based on what you discuss. I felt like he really cared about my physical and mental well-being and I wasn't just a name on a chart to him. Some of the therapies he uses, such as Ketamine or CBD, actually help the root cause of some issues, instead of just alleviating symptoms like many other things I have tried.

Robert Urban

I have known Dr. Rosado for a couple off years he was and will be my mothers Doctor for always. Let’s start by this doctor cares about his patients goes above and beyond for there needs and care. A very Great listener to understand what’s going on with you. I’m forever grateful God but him in our path when my mom was going through her cancer he was there all the way. We Love him this is the Best Doctor I’ve known. Recommend 200% his excellent in all he Does.

Daymer Lopez

Had a great experience as usual. The inside of the place and the parking lot are very well lit. The employees and nurses were helpful as always. The Doctor has so far Always provided an A to A+ experience and he takes the time to explain things to you. I would most likely recommend others visiting this place to see the Doctor if they are trying to find one

Benjamin Sanborn
